reviewText: Very short movie for the money.
Typical short Laurel and Hardy comedy.  Not as funny as others, but O.K.
One of the best comedy teams ever!
Short movie but great actors of comedy!
This is a good print of a fine Laurel & Hardy sound short. DVD is in good condition and it is the two-reel version (20 minutes).
This is a great classic L&H comedy. Includes a great performance by Charley Hall. If you can't laugh at this one, you need a laugh transplant.
